OL,3,CTwo newly trained police dogs boost
OL,4,Cdrug detection
OL,6,FTwo newly qualified specialist search
OL,7,Fdogs have been deployed to strengthen
OL,8,Fdrug enforcement efforts across
OL,9,FHampshire and the Isle of Wight.
OL,11,FAfter the pair completed an intensive
OL,12,Ftraining programme, they will now
OL,13,Fsupport officers in identifying and
OL,14,Fdisrupting illegal drug activity.
OL,16,FThis will include assisting at vehicle
OL,17,Fstops, search warrants and community
OL,18,Foperations.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/3
