OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1784879327
OL,3,CTwo newly trained police dogs boost
OL,4,Cdrug detection
OL,6,FHarry and Whitney will primarily play
OL,7,Fa key role in supporting frontline
OL,8,Fpolicing in Hampshire and the Isle of
OL,9,FWight, but will also be part of the
OL,10,FJoint Operations Unit and are capable
OL,11,Fof being deployed across the wider
OL,12,Fregion.
OL,14,FInspector Andy Mooge, Hampshire and
OL,15,FIsle of Wight Police, said: "Harry and
OL,16,FWhitney have shown fantastic potential
OL,17,Fthroughout their training. Their
OL,18,Fdeployment will significantly enhance
OL,19,Four ability to detect drugs and
OL,20,Fsupport operations across Hampshire
OL,21,Fand the Isle of Wight.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/3
